<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>20</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zhǔ de zhōng shēng 迦南20</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǐ jīng méi yǒu shí jiān zài xián zhàn, yǐ jīng méi yǒu xīn sī zài tān liàn,
 kuài bǎ jí dù fēn zhēng shì sú diū xià, nǐ kàn tiān lù shàng de rén men yǐ kuài zhàn mǎn
 kuài fā qǐ rè xīn yán zhe zhǔ de biāo gān, wàng jì bèi hòu nǔ lì miàn qián
 zhǔ de zhōng shēng zài ěr biān yī cì cì qiāo xiàng, nán dào nǐ réng chén shuì bù céng tīng jiàn?
 kuài sū xǐng ba shí jiān bù róng nǐ zài xián zhàn! kuài sū xǐng ba shí jiān bù róng nǐ zài tān liàn!
 nǐ tīng zhǔ de zhōng shēng yòu zài ěr biān qiāo xiǎng, tā shì zài cuī cù zhe nǐ wǒ kuài kuài xiàng qián!</lyrics>
</song>